GOOD HEART pursued from midpack two wide, but gave way along the inside around the far turn, and was eased up through the lane. THE RIDER OF SPY NOVEL CLAIMED FOUL AGAINST THE RIDER OF WICO (IRE) FOR INTERFERENCE IN MIDSTRETCH, BUT THE OBJECTION WAS DISALLOWED BY THE STEWARDS
